data.description: Must see ''Perdido Key'' model in active 55+ Vitalia at Tradition. This 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home also features an extended garage, an office (not counted as a bedroom) and upgraded landscaping. Great flow with the open floor plan. This is the perfect home to enjoy entertaining family & friends. Great view of the lake and pocket sliding doors leading to the screened in patio. The primary suite has a view of the lake, walk in closets, his and her sinks and a wide door. The open kitchen has granite counters, 42'' cabinets, large island, gas stove and a separate wine bar. Enjoy Vitalia's incredible clubhouse with resort style pool and spa, pickleball, tennis, bocce, billiards, and grand ballroom with professional entertainment, and more. Make an appointment to view this home today!
